        {
            "title": "聯儲會監管副主席稱銀行資本金改革計畫有望一季度末前推出",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會負責監管事務的副主席米歇爾·鮑曼周三表示，與巴塞爾協議III相關的修訂版銀行資本提案有望在第一季度結束前公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑曼在華盛頓Exchequer Club的活動上表示，美國監管機構計畫在今年晚些時候公佈該提案，然後徵求公眾意見。她強調，屆時將給予業界和公眾「充足時間」對方案進行評議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞社先前報導稱，監管機構正在制定新的銀行資本金提案，該方案將大幅放鬆拜登政府時期對華爾街大型銀行的擬議資本金要求。此前那一版本因遭到銀行業反對而未能最終敲定。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e4345d26-6199-3f56-a8fa-e07f9076ef42-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：聯儲會據悉醞釀新規 擬大幅放寬大型銀行報導的資本金上調要求</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑曼本周早些時候還表示，根據該提案，美國貸款機構料將面臨新的住房抵押貸款要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed Capital Plan Tied to Basel On Track for End of First Quarter</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E7%A8%B1%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%91%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B-%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%AB%E5%89%8D%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA-193911864.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 05:19:27",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯儲會會議紀要凸顯通膨擔憂 一些官員考慮潛在加息可能性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會官員對通膨表現出新的擔憂，多位政策制定者暗示，如果通膨持續高於目標，央行可能需要上調利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周三公佈的1月27至28日聯邦公開市場委員會(FOMC)會議紀要顯示，「幾位參與者暗示，他們本來打算支持對未來的利率路徑進行‘雙向’描述，以反映出如果通膨保持在目標水平之上，加息可能是適宜之舉。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紀要還透露，「絕大多數參與者認為，近幾個月就業面臨的下行風險已有所緩解，而通膨可能持久存在。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-51735e30-8149-324b-8413-e38f1c6aa0d0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本次會議上，FOMC以10比2的投票結果將基準聯邦基金利率維持在3.5%-3.75%區間。理事克里斯托弗·沃勒和斯蒂芬·米蘭投反對票，他們支持降息25個基點。官員們在聲明中刪除了前三次聲明中出現的關於就業下行風險增加的措辭。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紀要暗示，一部分政策制定者開始對進一步降息變得不那麼開放，至少短期內是這樣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紀要指出：「幾位參與者警告稱，在通膨居高不下的背景下進一步放鬆政策可能被誤解為決策者不再堅守控制通膨的承諾」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">幾位官員認為，如果通膨如預期般下降，有可能支持進一步降息，但大多數人表示，通膨改善的進程可能慢於普遍預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自1月會議以來，多位聯儲會政策制定者堅持認為，整體穩定的美國經濟使他們有餘地對利率調整保持耐心。川普及其他政府官員則繼續呼籲聯儲會立即降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易員今年已下調了對官員們下次降息時間的預期，不過聯邦基金期貨合約仍顯示下一次降息或發生在6月份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed Minutes Show Several Officials Point to Rate-Hike Scenario</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E7%B4%80%E8%A6%81%E5%87%B8%E9%A1%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-%E4%BA%9B%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-191301306.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 05:19:30",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人工智能時代或將削減對招聘人員的需求 人力資源巨頭面臨考驗",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: David Ryder/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e0CtIfbvB.hgbzhGgAnMqQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a29ef7c630b5122d8040f2abc570fbf4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: David Ryder/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>可能很快自動化處理候選人與雇主的匹配工作，從而減少對招聘人員的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人工智能的進步允許雇主在不依賴羅恆致富(Robert Half)、萬寶盛華集團(ManpowerGroup Inc.)、任仕達(Randstad NV)等公司外部招聘人員的情況下，完成簡歷篩選、申請人排序以及初步面試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著技術的提高和部署成本的降低，企業越來越有能力將部分招聘環節轉為內部處理。這加劇了該行業現有的挑戰，因為疫情後招聘熱潮已被「低離職、低招聘」的環境所取代。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c6098846-a107-39e3-98d7-a70622bcdf05-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於那些留下來的人來說，人工智能也可能使他們的工作複雜化。幫助候選人改寫或美化簡歷的工具可能會使申請人變得難以區分化。彭博行業研究高級分析師Stuart Gordon說：「每個人的履歷看起來都會一模一樣。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"在西雅圖的一場招聘會上，一名求職者正在與招聘人員交談。攝影：David Ryder/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6KdV4mV4p8mcqp_24l2Qgw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f965aaca44eb63ad295806c1e1354563\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">在西雅圖的一場招聘會上，一名求職者正在與招聘人員交談。攝影：David Ryder/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人力資源高管們反駁了人工智能可以完全取代招聘人員工作的觀點。羅恆致富執行長基思·瓦德爾在最近的業績電話會議上表示，人工智能對該公司的核心業務影響「微乎其微」，尤其是在中小客戶中。他補充說，人工智能使得簡歷的真實性更難驗證，增加了對招聘人員判斷力和個人互動的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師警告稱，人力資源公司不僅面臨初創公司的競爭，還面臨擁有資源利用人工智能構建或改進招聘平台的大型科技公司的競爭，微軟旗下LinkedIn就是一個例子。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前尚不清楚人工智能和自動化最終會摧毀工作崗位還是創造新崗位，目前的證據各異。許多公司在宣布裁員時提到了人工智能，但美國的失業率一直保持相對穩定。Gordon表示，需要持續的失業成長才能證明對就業產生了結構性影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">而這將進一步減少對招聘人員的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國巴黎銀行分析師安德魯·格羅布勒在12月下調了對德科集團、PageGroup Plc和羅恆致富的評級，稱臨時工從事自動化高風險崗位的可能性比整個勞動力市場高出40%。格羅布勒對德科的評級為「中性」，對PageGroup和羅恆致富的評級為「跑輸大盤」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x3jNy20gqIkQyUPrBfq.5Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a428f68218784a3f8c74ec8e7f047b5a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Your Next Job Offer May Come Via AI, Making Recruiters Redundant</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E6%88%96%E5%B0%87%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%8D%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%9B%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E8%80%83%E9%A9%97-154349113.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 00:24:17",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "未來10年值得持有的最佳科技股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ARXDoYMr3lNw2OJxNOPN1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/a53c765abcf2a54cce853350e7dbafb1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場焦點被少數大型科技股壟斷之際，仍有其他科技公司同樣值得投資者留意，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Broadcom;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Broadcom\">Broadcom</a>（AVGO）便是當中之一。這家公司由傳統網絡及軟件企業，蛻變為與全球頂級雲端巨頭合作的尖端AI客製晶片供應商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Broadcom與同業的最大分別，在於其極強的財務實力；公司目前自由現金流約74億美元，既能持續派息，亦有充足資金支持未來增長，而最新業績進一步鞏固「Broadcom是業績火車頭」的市場印象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在2025年第四季度，Broadcom收入按年增長28%，自由現金流則按年上升36%；即使增長未來略為放緩，穩健的資產負債表仍為公司建立深厚護城河。公司亦在最近宣布把股息再提高10%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-59ab43b2-11fb-3e95-a009-18803f612bd3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Broadcom股價歷來波動不小，但耐心持有的投資者最終獲得豐厚回報；截至2月11日，該股12個月升幅約45%，過去5年累計更升615%，市值增加至逾1萬億美元，跻身全球市值最高企業之列。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更重要的是，Broadcom擁有極強執行力，現時手上高達1620億美元訂單，足以支撐公司未來10年的持續增長動能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作者：Catie Hogan, The Fool</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 HKMoneyClub</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多你或感興趣內容：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/14/%e9%87%8d%e6%ba%ab%e3%80%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%a3%87%e9%95%b7%e6%af%9b%e3%80%8ddavid-webb%e7%9a%848%e5%a4%a7%e9%95%b7%e7%b7%9a%e8%87%b4%e5%8b%9d%e6%b3%95%e5%89%87/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/28/%e7%99%bd%e9%8a%802025%e5%b9%b4%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%87144-%e4%bd%86%e6%ad%b7%e5%8f%b2%e6%9a%97%e7%a4%ba2026%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%96%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/30/%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83ai%e6%b3%a1%e6%b2%ab%e7%88%86%e7%a0%b4%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%993%e7%a8%ae%e8%bc%83%e7%a9%a9%e9%99%a3%e7%9a%84%e9%81%b8%e6%93%87%e5%8f%af%e7%82%ba%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e7%b5%84%e5%90%88/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">睇完新聞，記得追蹤hkmoneyclub以下平台，接收更多分析評論！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">YouTube：hkmoneyclub (https://www.youtube.com/@hkmoneyclub)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本文所提供的信息僅供一般參考之用，並不構成任何個人化的投資勸誘或建議。作者沒持有以上提及的股票。 HK MoneyClub (www.hkmoneyclub.com)</p></div>",
